title: [Airiella's Magic Shoppe]
description: Beneath an uneven wooden ceiling, a tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the plain wooden walls.  A plain wooden table sits in one corner while a worn rug rests on the wooden floor.

Beneath an uneven wooden ceiling, a tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the plain wooden walls.  A large cherrywood cabinet and a plain wooden table sit in opposite corners while a worn rug rests on an unfinished wooden floor.
